channel.title: Monitor session logs :: My New Hugo Site
channel.description: Monitor session logs Access System Manager - Session Manager service management console Click the Preferences tab. Click Edit. Scroll down, at S3 logging, click Enable. Uncheck Allow only encrypted S3 buckets. Click Choose a bucket name from the list. Select the S3 bucket you created. Scroll down, click Save to save the configuration.

item.title: Theo dõi session logs
item.description: Theo dõi session logs Truy cập giao diện quản trị dịch vụ System Manager - Session Manager Click tab Preferences. Click Edit. Kéo chuột xuống phía dưới, tại mục S3 logging, click chọn Enable. Bỏ chọn Allow only encrypted S3 buckets. Click chọn Choose a bucket name from the list. Chọn S3 bucket bạn đã tạo.
